      <hedline>
        <hl1>NO LAYOFFS, G.M. PROMISES DAEWOO</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Samuel Len</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Len, Samuel</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>General Motors Corp chairman Jack Smith, vowing there will be no layoffs at Daewoo Motor Co, tries to win support for its bid to acquire ailing South Korean automaker; rival bidder Ford Motor has made similar promises (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Vowing there would be no layoffs at the Daewoo Motor Company, Jack Smith, the chairman of General Motors, tried to win support for its bid to acquire the ailing South Korean carmaker. The rival bidder Ford Motor has made similar promises.</p>
        <p>Samuel Len</p>
      </block>
